entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You talked to the mayor and he's got you helping with some local issues.
entries.journal_entry_description: Bib wants you to talk the mayor about some work he needs done.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Ahh...the troublemaker! Jabba is not pleased with you. Go see the Mayor. If you can help him pay Jabba it might buy you some mercy.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Vourk said Bib would be calling you soon.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Bib has told you the Mayor needs some work done.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: The Mayor has work that will help you work into Jabba's favor.
